<br>
<br>
&gt;| Dumb Question 1: Does there exist a parallel system of<br>
&gt;| reservation for non-planes encounters? Such as Vox,<br>
&gt;| Nagafen, Gorenaire, Venril Sathir and the remaining<br>
&gt;| Dragonship Connection (George Clinton reference, think<br>
